title: Gummersall's Time To Shine
text:
Tanner Gummersall has waited for his opportunity to 
be a factor for Central Valley. 
Now that his time is here, he's making the most of 
it. 
Gummersall is leading the way for the Bears football 
team both on the field and in the classroom. 
He's the subject of this week's Kimmel Athletic Shining 
Star. 
If you would like to nominate a Shining Star, they 
have to be a senior with at least a 3.5 GPA, please 
send us a nomination to our e-mail address: Sports@700espn.com Spokane, Wash. -
